title: Dakine Anya Shoulder Bag
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Anya Shoulder Bag in our Feather print.
Anya Features:
- Interior fleece lined padded laptop sleeve
- Fits most 15” Laptops
- Zipper closure
- Vinyl trims and handles
- Adjustable and removable cross body shoulder strap
- Metal hardware
- Interior zippered pocket
- Interior organizer pockets-
- Nylon lining
